{"tid":880124,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美航母30年來首入北極 參加挪威軍演","createTime":"2018-10-28T13:55:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T00:49:16.000Z","uid":141151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5905b1b87950a5252d92aee0c7d880fcafaab31e","tid":880124,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T13:55:08.000Z","msg":"美航母30年來首入北極 參加挪威軍演<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181020002006-260417\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20181020002006-260417&d=S3hZbgsybcF0tVxnO%2BU3IJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=c10958eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20181020002006-260417</a><br />\n<br />\n美國核動力航空母艦杜魯門號於當地時間19日，越過北極圈進入北極，這是美國核動力航空母艦自1991年以來，首次再度進入北極。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國海軍新聞處稱，由杜魯門號航空母艦率領的航母突擊編隊隨後將前往挪威海，以「展示美國海軍的機動性和硬實力」。這些艦隻也將與此前在冰島海岸登陸的2000名美國海軍陸戰隊隊員，一起參加北約在10月底於挪威舉行的「三叉戟」軍演。<br />\n<br />\n上一次美國海軍航空母艦美國號航母進入到北極水域，是在1991年參加了「北極星」軍演。"},{"pid":"e2e68347a5f7266f0b6df5ff3e5932331ce03fb7","tid":880124,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-28T14:35:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15d802b96269f8e11367977c84e550c702b6b0ac","tid":880124,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T00:49:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}